'''''Challenge'' 72''' was a roleplaying magazine from October [[1993]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including an adventure for the [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game|D6]] system. The article was called "[[Ananuru Express (article)|''Ananuru Express'']]" and was written by [[Alison Brooks]].

